features: Air fryer protectors - You put it on the Ninja Toaster Oven crumbs tray and it collects grease spills and crumbs. Size is perfect (30x30 cm/12x12 inch). Super easy to clean. No smell on high temperatures.

Great time saver - These oven fryer liners will save you countless evenings of scrubbing your drip pans. Dripping simply rinse off. Make cleanup a snap. These liners fit Ninja Foodi SP101 SP201 perfectly. Perfect liner for air fryer, toaster ovens.

Our oven liners are made of high-quality fiberglass with a special coating on the surface. Reusable, double-sided use, good heat resistance, durable. It's eliminated my use of disposable traditional baking grease paper and unlike the paper it doesn't burn, smell, or discolor over time.

Air fry oven liners are super easy to cut and fit whatever width/length you need. After cutting, please use a lighter to remove the cut white edges to avoid starting a fire on the grill. These are versatile and can be used as oven liners, pan liners, baking/cooking sheets and grill mats.

Easy to clean (soap & water) and dishwasher safe. They are durable and reusable. If there is a problem with the product received, we will replace it with a new oven liner. If you don't like it, feel free to return it for a refund.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good Liners If You Need 12×12 and Tongs Are a Plus!
reviews.reviewText: I am using them in a Cuisinart TOA-95 AirFryer Toaster Oven.I have used them for toast and for air frying fish fillets, hashbrown patties, hot dogs, tater tots, boiled eggs, french fries and a few other things, I have used them on the rack, in the pan, and in the pan with the basket on top for air frying. A lot of the cooking was done at 400, and 450 degrees, without any problems. They did not smell, or smoke. They clean up great. When rinsing, the water flows off instantly, with very little drying needed.I tried one on the crumb tray, but when using preheat it was only 1 inch below the heating element which was too close and did not seem safe as it was not looking right. Better safe than sorry, but I did not need one on it anyway because the liners kept crumbs and such from falling on it.I have a couple of different types of real good tongs, so I sure was not expecting to like the ones that come with these liners, but boy was I wrong. These tongs being much smaller, are working out great for using with my air fryer toaster oven! They are good enough for my needs and I am glad to have them.I really need a 12×14 inch or more liner for cutting to the size that I want, but I ordered these anyway, and have been very surprised at how good they are. I like them a lot. I have found nothing wrong with these liners and will keep using them, but I will also be getting some larger ones to cut to the sizes that I want.These are too good to not keep them. I cook a few things that these will be good to use for.I thought that the liners sounded too good to be true, but I would give them a try, and it was true.You should be happy with these if a 12×12 liner is the size that will work for you.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I use this item almost everyday
reviews.reviewText: I use my Ninja Foodi multiple times a week, especially the air fryer feature. I bought some parchment paper liners for the basket, but was going through them so fast, so I was happy to see these reusable mats. I trimmed a couple to fit the basket and punched holes in one. I have been using them for several days and they work wonderfully! Food cooks great, there is zero odor from the mat, and clean-up is quick and easy. I used one to line a small baking sheet that I use in the oven, so now it is a breeze to clean up, also. I am so happy with this product!
